    "content_list_gempnj": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "image_RNWGRr": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p><br/><strong>Curating Your Bridal Look</strong></p><p>As you begin curating the pieces you'll wear on your wedding day, consider how each element speaks to the next. The silhouette of your gown. The way your hair is styled. The details that feel most like you.</p><p>A high neckline may ask for little more than a sculptural earring, paired with a bracelet. A clean, open neckline creates space for a necklace to become part of the story, drawing the eye and complimenting your gown. </p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p><br/><strong>Curating Your Bridal Look</strong></p><p>As you begin curating the pieces you'll wear on your wedding day, consider how each element speaks to the next. The silhouette of your gown. The way your hair is styled. The details that feel most like you.</p><p>A high neckline may ask for little more than a sculptural earring, paired with a bracelet. A clean, open neckline creates space for a necklace to become part of the story, drawing the eye and complimenting your gown. </p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
