    "800eebd7-962e-4fa6-bc5d-8b818a1ba455": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "template--16177341137065__800eebd7-962e-4fa6-bc5d-8b818a1ba455-image-1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p><strong>A Few Styling Considerations</strong></p><p>While there are no rules when it comes to bridal jewellery, these considerations can help guide your edit:</p><p>— Intricate or high necklines often pair beautifully with statement earrings and a refined bracelet.</p><p>— Open, strapless or sweetheart necklines create space for a necklace to become part of the story.</p><p>— Hair worn up allows earrings to take centre stage. </p><p>— Hair worn down may call for pieces with more movement, length and presence.</p><p>— When in doubt, choose one hero piece and allow it to draw the eye. </p><p>The most considered bridal edits are often the most effortless. Thoughtfully chosen pieces that complement your gown, reflect your personal style and feel true to you. Choose pieces that feel timeless. Pieces that feel personal and the designs you'll treasure long beyond the wedding day, carrying the memory of where your story began.</p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p><strong>A Few Styling Considerations</strong></p><p>While there are no rules when it comes to bridal jewellery, these considerations can help guide your edit:</p><p>— Intricate or high necklines often pair beautifully with statement earrings and a refined bracelet.</p><p>— Open, strapless or sweetheart necklines create space for a necklace to become part of the story.</p><p>— Hair worn up allows earrings to take centre stage. </p><p>— Hair worn down may call for pieces with more movement, length and presence.</p><p>— When in doubt, choose one hero piece and allow it to draw the eye. </p><p>The most considered bridal edits are often the most effortless. Thoughtfully chosen pieces that complement your gown, reflect your personal style and feel true to you. Choose pieces that feel timeless. Pieces that feel personal and the designs you'll treasure long beyond the wedding day, carrying the memory of where your story began.</p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
